Belle Rises in Manila After Vice Chairman Ocier Acquires Shares

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-14T02:58:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/belle-rises-in-manila-after-vice-chairman-ocier-acquires-shares.html
Belle Corp. (BEL)  climbed as much as 5
percent in Manila trading after Vice Chairman Willy Ocier
acquired 133,238 shares of the company, a Philippine Stock
Exchange filing showed.  The stock gained 2.2 percent to 3.70 pesos as of 10:43 a.m.
local time. The benchmark Philippine Stock Exchange Index
increased 0.4 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Allen Wan at 
 awan3@bloomberg.net  